The evidence with the title 'Repeal the obamacare taxes | aier ' says May 17, 2017  ... “ obamacare contains 20 new or higher taxes on American families and small businesses, ” writes John Kartch of Americans For Tax Reform. Kartch notes that Obamacare authorized “ $500 billion-plus in tax hikes (over the next ten years). ”ATR later estimated that the taxes would amount to over $1 trillion. 
